      <div class="platform-card reveal"><div class="platform-icon" style="background:rgba(20,184,166,.15)">⚛️</div><div class="platform-name">React + Tailwind</div><div class="platform-desc">SPAs, SSR y web apps de alta performance con sistema de diseño a medida.</div><div class="platform-chips"><span class="pchip">React 18</span><span class="pchip">Tailwind</span><span class="pchip">Next.js</span><span class="pchip">Vite</span></div></div>
      <div class="platform-card reveal"><div class="platform-icon" style="background:rgba(2,132,199,.15)">💙</div><div class="platform-name">Flutter · Dart</div><div class="platform-desc">Apps nativas de alta fidelidad para iOS y Android desde una base de código.</div><div class="platform-chips"><span class="pchip">Flutter 3</span><span class="pchip">Dart</span><span class="pchip">Riverpod</span><span class="pchip">Bloc</span></div></div>
      <div class="platform-card reveal"><div class="platform-icon" style="background:rgba(239,68,68,.12)">🍎</div><div class="platform-name">Swift · SwiftUI</div><div class="platform-desc">Experiencias iOS nativas con HealthKit, ARKit y StoreKit integrados.</div><div class="platform-chips"><span class="pchip">Swift 5.9</span><span class="pchip">SwiftUI</span><span class="pchip">UIKit</span><span class="pchip">Combine</span></div></div>
      <div class="platform-card reveal"><div class="platform-icon" style="background:rgba(91,79,207,.15)">🎨</div><div class="platform-name">Design Systems</div><div class="platform-desc">Tokens compartidos. Figma como fuente única de verdad para todas las plataformas.</div><div class="platform-chips"><span class="pchip">Figma Tokens</span><span class="pchip">Storybook</span><span class="pchip">Style Dict</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TOKEN PLAYGROUND -->
<section id="playground">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">// Playground interactivo</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Cambia los tokens.<br>Ve el impacto en vivo.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead reveal">Ajusta colores, tipografía y radios. El cambio se refleja en web, iOS y Flutter simultáneamente — y genera el código listo para usar en cada plataforma.</p>
    <div class="playground-wrap">
      <div class="playground-controls reveal">
        <div class="ctrl-section">
          <span class="ctrl-label">Colores</span>
          <div class="ctrl-row"><span class="ctrl-name">color.primary</span><div class="ctrl-swatch" id="sw1"><div class="ctrl-bg" id="bg1" style="background:#1a1a2e"></div><input type="color" value="#1a1a2e" id="cp" oninput="upd()"></div></div>
          <div class="ctrl-row"><span class="ctrl-name">color.accent</span><div class="ctrl-swatch" id="sw2"><div class="ctrl-bg" id="bg2" style="background:#c8572a"></div><input type="color" value="#c8572a" id="ca" oninput="upd()"></div></div>
          <div class="ctrl-row"><span class="ctrl-name">color.surface</span><div class="ctrl-swatch" id="sw3"><div class="ctrl-bg" id="bg3" style="background:#f5f3ef"></div><input type="color" value="#f5f3ef" id="cs2" oninput="upd()"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ctrl-section">
          <span class="ctrl-label">Forma y tamaño</span>
          <div class="range-row"><label>radius.lg <span id="rv">12</span>px</label><input type="range" min="0" max="32" value="12" step="2" id="rr" oninput="upd()"></div>
          <div class="range-row"><label>font.size <span id="sv">16</span>px</label><input type="range" min="12" max="22" value="16" step="1" id="rs" oninput="upd()"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ctrl-section">
          <span class="ctrl-label">Tipografía</span>
          <div class="sel-row"><label>font.display</label><select id="sf" onchange="upd()"><option value="'Syne',sans-serif">Syne</option><option value="'DM Serif Display',serif">DM Serif</option><option value="'DM Mono',monospace">DM Mono</option><option value="Georgia,serif">Georgia</option></select></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ctrl-section">
          <span class="ctrl-label">Código generado</span>
          <div class="code-tab-row">
            <button class="code-tab active" onclick="swCode('tw',this)">Tailwind</button>
            <button class="code-tab" onclick="swCode('fl',this)">Flutter</button>
            <button class="code-tab" onclick="swCode('sw',this)">SwiftUI</button>
          </div>
          <div class="code-out" id="cout"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="playground-preview">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="preview-label">Web — React + Tailwind</div>
          <div class="preview-panel">
            <div class="pv-topbar"><div class="pv-dot" style="background:#ff5f56"></div><div class="pv-dot" style="background:#ffbd2e"></div><div class="pv-dot" style="background:#27c93f"></div></div>
            <div class="pv-body">
              <div id="wcard" style="border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;background:#f5f3ef;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08)">
                <div id="whead" style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:.4rem;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;color:#0e0e0e">Título del componente</div>
                <div id="wbody" style="font-size:16px;color:#6b6b6b;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:.75rem">Texto con los tokens aplicados en tiempo real. Cambia los controles y observa el impacto en todas las plataformas.</div>
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
                  <button id="wbtn" style="background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:.55rem 1.3rem;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif">Acción →</button>
                  <span id="wbadge" style="background:#c8572a;color:#fff;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;padding:.25rem .6rem;border-radius:4px">token activo</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="preview-label">Mobile — Flutter + SwiftUI</div>
          <div class="mpv-wrap">
            <div class="mpv-frame">
              <div class="mpv-notch"><div class="mpv-pill"></div></div>
              <div class="mpv-body">
                <div id="fcard" style="background:#f5f3ef;border-radius:10px;padding:.75rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06)">
                  <div id="fhead" style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#0e0e0e;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;margin-bottom:.25rem">Flutter Widget</div>
                  <div id="fbody" style="font-size:11px;color:#6b6b6b;line-height:1.6">Mismos tokens exportados vía Style Dictionary.</div>
                </div>
                <button id="fbtn" style="width:100%;background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;padding:.5rem;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif">Acción →</button>
                <div style="display:flex;gap:.35rem;margin-top:.5rem">
                  <span id="ft1" style="font-size:10px;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:99px;background:#e8f0fe;color:#1a56db;font-family:var(--mono)">flutter</span>
                  <span id="ft2" style="font-size:10px;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:99px;background:#eee;color:#555;font-family:var(--mono)">dart</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mpv-frame">
              <div class="mpv-notch"><div class="mpv-pill"></div></div>
              <div class="mpv-body">
                <div id="scard" style="background:#f5f3ef;border-radius:10px;padding:.75rem;margin-bottom:.5rem">
                  <div id="shead" style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#0e0e0e;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;margin-bottom:.25rem">SwiftUI View</div>
                  <div id="sbody" style="font-size:11px;color:#6b6b6b;line-height:1.6">Tokens Swift generados automáticamente desde el mismo JSON.</div>
                </div>
                <button id="sbtn" style="width:100%;background:#c8572a;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;padding:.5rem;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif">iOS Button</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

